{
  "name": "Ring of the Endless Hunt",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>(Requires attunement by a creature)</em></p><p>This ring is rumored to have been worn by the finest archers of Yenlara. Whenever a bow is drawn by the hand wearing this ring, a nonmagical arrow springs forth, nocked and ready to fire. The arrow evaporates into a harmless mist after 1 minute.</p><p><strong>Requires Attunement:</strong> If you attune to this ring, then attacks made by a bow treat the bow as if it is a +1 magic weapon.  This magical bonus does not stack with another bow with a bonus to hit and damage.</p>",
